ower systems are monitored and controlled."</i>".</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=State+Estimation+and+Voltage+Security+Monitoring+Using+Synchronized+Phasor+Measurement&amp;rft.jtitle=Research+paper+from+work+sponsored+by+American+Electric+Power%2C+ABB+Power+T%26D+Company%2C+and+%5B%5BTennessee+Valley+Authority%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Yilu+Liu%2C+Lamine+Mili%2C+Jaime+De+La+Ree%2C+Reynaldo+Francisco+Nuqui%2C+Reynaldo+Francisco+Nuqui&amp;rft.au=Yilu+Liu%2C+Lamine+Mili%2C+Jaime+De+La+Ree%2C+Reynaldo+Francisco+Nuqui%2C+Reynaldo+Francisco+Nuqui&amp;rft.date=2001-07-12&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BVirginia+Polytechnic+Institute+and+State+University%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fciteseerx.ist.psu.edu%2Fviewdoc%2Fdownload%3Bjsessionid%3D3B975B94733D906CA197813C53C2BD86%3Fdoi%3D10.1.1.2.7959%26rep%3Drep1%26type%3Dpdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Smart_grid"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
